TestCase_00016_dr_test_mobiload ( )
Trusted Applications dependencies:
none
Focus:
Check if Mobiload can successfully load a driver(DrTestMobiload). Mobiload is a feature added in grub or uboot bootloader, containing a Driver which is loaded before the rich os starts.
Test Steps:
Open session to TATestDrApi TATestDrApi call drDrApiTestMobiload(), a DrTestMobiload API This API uses the IPC and the session management of DrTestMobiload If no session Id is returned, the TA returns an error and the test fails
Manual Execution:
No

No

Extensive Testcase:
Yes
Basic Testcase:

Quick Testcase:
No
Minimum Product Version required for this testcase:
